PN,41901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1773745530
OL,3,CTwo dead after outbreak of 'invasive'
OL,4,Cdisease reported at university
OL,6,FTwo people have died and several more
OL,7,Fare in hospital, following an outbreak
OL,8,Fof an "invasive" disease at the
OL,9,FUniversity of Kent.
OL,11,FHealth officials say they are aware of
OL,12,F13 cases of invasive meningococcal
OL,13,Fdisease in the Canterbury area since
OL,14,FFriday, but the specific strain isn't
OL,15,Fyet known.
OL,17,FMeningococcal disease a rapidly
OL,18,Fprogressing bacterial infection, which
OL,19,Foften leads to conditions such as
OL,20,Fmeningitis and septicaemia.
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
